lenders.loan_because: Rezokem Inc is involved in the community by sharing a portion of their profit with Kiva to help people in need around the world
lenders.occupational_info: We are a canadian based company specialized in the distribution of biorenewable ressources to the polyurethane industry.  We believe in non crude oil based ressources like castor oil as a viable raw material for the formulation of ''green'' polyurethane foam, coating and adhesive.
